  "content": {
    "prompt": "Construct a program that determines whether an integer is even or odd.",
    "source_code": "#Step 1: Read the integer \ntext = input(\"Enter an integer: \")\nnum = int(text)       \n#Step 2: Determine whether the integer is even or odd\nif num % 2 == 0 : \n    print(\"The integer is even.\") \nelse :\n    print(\"The integer is odd.\") "
